pageContext.claim: “If Biden got in, you'd be paying $7, $8, $9, then they'll say, 'Get rid of your car.'”
pageContext.analysis: Gas prices would increase over time if all of Biden’s environmental proposals are put into effect though there is significant dispute over how much. At the high end, one Trump loyalist suggested it could be as much as $6.00 or $7.00, but most estimates are below that.
